pkgmetadata.longdescription: Supplemental U. S. 2010 Census Tract Boundaries for 15 States with Seer Registries for 'SeerMapper' // Provides supplemental 2010 census tract boundaries of the 15 states containing Seer Registries for use with the 'SeerMapper' package. The data contained in this package is derived from U. S. 2010 Census data and is in public domain.
